Mario Kart
==================

This is a Mario Kart map made using Charli's Mario Kart prefab.

It is my first attempt at making a Mario Kart map so it may be a little basic, but if feed back is good I will make something more themed.

CT's can be Mario or Luigi and Ts can be Wario or Bowser.

There are boosts around the map and obstacles to tangle with.

Constructive feedback is always appreciated!
